query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `organization_settings` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY,
  `organizationId` int NOT NULL,
  `shareClients` tinyint NOT NULL DEFAULT 1,
  `sharePianos` tinyint NOT NULL DEFAULT 1,
  `shareInventory` tinyint NOT NULL DEFAULT 1,
  `shareAgenda` tinyint NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  `shareInvoices` tinyint NOT NULL DEFAULT 1,
  `shareQuotes` tinyint NOT NULL DEFAULT 1,
  `membersCanViewOthersClients` tinyint NOT NULL DEFAULT 1,
  `membersCanEditOthersClients` tinyint NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  `membersCanViewOthersServices` tinyint NOT NULL DEFAULT 1,
  `membersCanViewOthersInvoices` tinyint NOT NULL DEFAULT 1,
  `autoAssignServices` tinyint NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  `requireApprovalForInvoices` tinyint NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `updatedAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  INDEX `organization_settings_org_unique` (`organizationId`)
);
